OL,7,FEarlier on Saturday, MPs and peers had
OL,8,Fapproved emergency legislation without
OL,9,Fopposition, giving Mr Reynolds the
OL,10,Fpower to require British Steel to keep
OL,11,Fthe Scunthorpe plant going after talks
OL,12,Fwith its Chinese owner, Jingye, broke
OL,13,Fdown.
OL,15,FThe prime minister told British Steel
OL,16,Fworkers the government had "control
OL,17,Fnow."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
