OL,7,F"This is legislation in the national
OL,8,Finterest," the prime minister said, as
OL,9,Fhe promised to, "keep the blast
OL,10,Ffurnaces on."
OL,12,FWriting in The Sunday Times, Mr
OL,13,FReynolds said the Government "refused
OL,14,Fto be extorted by a company that
OL,15,Frepeatedly refused to act rationally".
OL,17,F"The seeds of this decision were sown
OL,18,Flong before the United States opted to
OL,19,Fimpose tariffs on steel," he said.
