OL,7,F"Previous governments have been too
OL,8,Fwilling to stand idly by while heat
OL,9,Fseeped out of blast furnaces, but to
OL,10,Flose this capability now, in this
OL,11,Fmanner, would have weakened our
OL,12,Findustrial base irrevocably. Inaction
OL,13,Fwas never an option."
OL,15,FBusinesses and trade unions welcomed
OL,16,Fthe government's decision to take
OL,17,Fcontrol of the Scunthorpe plant.
