OL,7,FJohn Foster, chief policy and
OL,8,Fcampaigns officer at the CBI, said it
OL,9,Fwas "a necessary outcome of last
OL,10,Fresort" to protect the UK's primary
OL,11,Fsteelmaking industry, while TUC
OL,12,Fgeneral secretary Paul Nowak said it
OL,13,Fwas "the right thing to do" and "in
OL,14,Fthe national interest".
OL,16,FThe Steel Industry (Special Measures)
OL,17,FBill gives the business secretary the
OL,18,Fpowers to prevent the Chinese owner of
OL,19,Fthe plant, Jingye, from closing blast
OL,20,Ffurnaces at the site.
