OL,7,FThe Bill, which the government
OL,8,Fpublished ahead of the debate on
OL,9,FSaturday, allows the government to
OL,10,Finstruct steel companies to keep
OL,11,Fassets running, and to take over those
OL,12,Fassets if they fail to comply with
OL,13,Fthose instructions.
OL,15,FIt also provides for a compensation
OL,16,Fscheme for costs incurred by the
OL,17,Fcompany following the government's
OL,18,Finstructions, and criminal sanctions
OL,19,Ffor executives who disregard them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
