OL,7,FMr Reynolds said the legislation is
OL,8,F"unequivocally in our national
OL,9,Finterests". The Leader of the Commons,
OL,10,FLucy Powell, urged MPs to act
OL,11,F"decisively" and "at a pace" to ensure
OL,12,Ffurnaces are kept going to save the
OL,13,Fdomestic production of virgin steel.
OL,15,FBut Alex Burghart, who was acting as
OL,16,Fshadow Commons leader, told MPs the
OL,17,Fgovernment had "made a total pig's
OL,18,Fbreakfast of the whole arrangement."
