OL,7,F"The fact of the matter is anyone who
OL,8,Fhas been paying any attention to this
OL,9,Fstory over the past few months has
OL,10,Fknown this was coming down the track,"
OL,11,Fhe said.
OL,13,FJingye said the business is running at
OL,14,Fa loss of #700,000 a day maintaining
OL,15,Fthe plant. They claim the plant's two
OL,16,Fblast furnaces are no longer
OL,17,Ffinancially sustainable and the raw
OL,18,Fmaterials needed to keep them
OL,19,Foperational are running out.
