OL,7,FParliament was recalled to sit on
OL,8,FSaturday - for the first time since
OL,9,F1982 - to discuss how the government
OL,10,Fcan save the UK's last virgin steel
OL,11,Fplant.
OL,13,FThe business secretary described the
OL,14,Flegislation as a "proportionate and
OL,15,Fnecessary step," telling MPs it would
OL,16,F"allow us to take control of British
OL,17,FSteel's blast furnaces, maintaining
OL,18,Fsteel production and by extension
OL,19,Fprotecting the company's 3,500-strong
OL,20,Fworkforce."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
