OL,7,FThe business secretary stressed that
OL,8,Fthe measures, while they would allow
OL,9,Fthe government to "take control of the
OL,10,Fsituation", would be "temporary."
OL,12,F"I do not want these powers any minute
OL,13,Flonger than is necessary, but I do
OL,14,Fneed these powers to rectify and save
OL,15,Fthis situation," he said.
